OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for most with
OL,6,Fthe odd shower. Brightening up for
OL,7,Fsome by the afternoon but heavy slow-
OL,8,Fmoving showers may develop across
OL,9,FPembrokeshire and Carmarthenshire.
OL,10,FFeeling somewhat cooler in the light
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers continuing overnight,
OL,14,Fheaviest in the southwest. Some clear
OL,15,Fspells in places but temperatures
OL,16,Fstaying above freezing for most areas,
OL,17,Fbut a patchy frost developing in rural
OL,18,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
