OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry start to the
OL,6,Fday but more cloud developing through
OL,7,Fthe morning which will develop into
OL,8,Ffurther showers into the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FScattered
OL,11,Fshowers on Friday, mainly in the
OL,12,Fafternoons, but staying dry for some.
OL,13,FLonger periods of rain are possible on
OL,14,FSaturday and Sunday. Turning warmer
OL,15,Fafter chilly nights at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
